-- Sunderland Beats Southampton to Reach League Cup Quarterfinals
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2013-11-06T22:04:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-06/sunderland-beats-southampton-to-reach-league-cup-quarterfinals.html
Sunderland beat Southampton 2-1 to
advance to the quarterfinals of English soccer’s League Cup.  Phil Bardsley and Sebastian Larsson scored for Sunderland,
which will meet Chelsea in the final eight of  England ’s second-tier cup competition. Maya Yoshida scored for Southampton.  Manchester City visits Leicester City, Stoke hosts
Manchester United and West Ham is at Tottenham to complete the
quarterfinal round, which will be played Dec. 17 and 18.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
